---
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Experience | Ron Keesing"
  description="More than twenty years of experience leading enterprise AI, integrating advanced technology, and advancing applied AI research."
>
  <Header activePage="experience" />

  <main>
    <section class="page-introduction">
      <div class="site-container">
        <h1>Experience</h1>

        <p>
          For more than twenty years, I have helped organizations apply
          artificial intelligence to complex, mission-critical challenges. My
          experience spans advanced AI research, enterprise technology
          leadership, and executive responsibility for AI strategy, governance,
          and transformation. Throughout that journey, the focus has remained
          consistent: translating emerging AI capabilities into trusted
          operational systems that deliver measurable results.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="experience-sections site-container">
      <section
        class="experience-section"
        aria-labelledby="enterprise-ai-heading"
      >
        <header class="section-introduction">
          <h2 id="enterprise-ai-heading">Leading Enterprise AI</h2>

          <p class="section-subtitle">
            Establishing enterprise AI strategy, governance, and organizational
            transformation.
          </p>

          <p class="section-summary">
            As Leidos' first Chief AI Officer, I established the enterprise AI
            operating model and led AI strategy across a $17B Fortune 300
            company serving defense, intelligence, healthcare, energy,
            transportation, and civilian agencies. Responsibilities included
            enterprise AI strategy, Trusted AI governance, AI investment,
            executive advising, workforce enablement, and deployment of
            generative and agentic AI at scale.
          </p>
        </header>

        <div class="highlights">
          <h3>Highlights</h3>

          <ul>
            <li>
              Created the enterprise AI operating model spanning five business
              sectors and corporate functions.
            </li>

            <li>
              Directed an annual AI investment portfolio of approximately
              $40 million.
            </li>

            <li>
              Established the company's Trusted AI governance framework and
              chaired the Enterprise AI Governance Board.
            </li>

            <li>
              Guided enterprise adoption of generative and agentic AI, enabling
              secure deployment across highly regulated environments.
            </li>

            <li>
              Reported AI strategy, risk, and progress to executive leadership
              and the Board of Directors.
            </li>

            <li>
              Helped deliver approximately $50 million in annual AI-enabled
              value across customer programs and internal operations.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section
        class="experience-section"
        aria-labelledby="technology-integration-heading"
      >
        <header class="section-introduction">
          <h2 id="technology-integration-heading">
            Leading Technology Integration
          </h2>

          <p class="section-subtitle">
            Integrating and delivering AI, cyber, software, and digital
            modernization to solve complex mission challenges.
          </p>

          <p class="section-summary">
            Before becoming Chief AI Officer, I spent five years building the
            organizational and technical capabilities that enabled enterprise
            AI transformation. I founded the Leidos AI Accelerator, later
            established the Technology Integration organization, and led
            multidisciplinary teams responsible for integrating AI, cyber,
            software engineering, and digital modernization into enterprise
            solutions and customer programs.
          </p>
        </header>

        <div class="highlights">
          <h3>Highlights</h3>

          <ul>
            <li>
              Founded the Leidos AI Accelerator and built a team of more than
              50 AI scientists, engineers, and solution architects.
            </li>

            <li>
              Created the Technology Integration organization, growing it to
              more than 250 scientists, engineers, and technologists.
            </li>

            <li>
              Directed approximately $30 million annually in internal
              technology investment.
            </li>

            <li>
              Supported more than $40 billion in competitive pursuits by
              integrating advanced technologies into enterprise solutions.
            </li>

            <li>
              Accelerated the transition of generative AI from experimentation
              to operational deployment across the company.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section
        class="experience-section"
        aria-labelledby="ai-research-heading"
      >
        <header class="section-introduction">
          <h2 id="ai-research-heading">Leading AI Research</h2>

          <p class="section-subtitle">
            Advancing artificial intelligence through applied research and
            operational innovation.
          </p>

          <p class="section-summary">
            Long before generative AI became mainstream, I led research and
            development programs exploring machine learning, knowledge
            discovery, autonomous systems, predictive analytics, and decision
            support for some of the U.S. government's most demanding technical
            organizations. These efforts established the technical foundation
            that later informed my work leading enterprise AI.
          </p>
        </header>

        <div class="highlights">
          <h3>Representative areas of work</h3>

          <ul>
            <li>Machine learning and knowledge extraction</li>
            <li>Knowledge graphs and semantic technologies</li>
            <li>Autonomous systems and human-machine teaming</li>
            <li>Predictive analytics and decision support</li>
            <li>
              AI applications for national security and scientific discovery
            </li>
          </ul>

          <p class="organizations">
            Programs supported organizations including DARPA, IARPA, DIA, DTRA,
            SOCOM, ONR, and the U.S. Army.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .page-introduction {
    padding:
      clamp(3.5rem, 6vw, 5.5rem) 0
      clamp(3.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
  }

  .page-introduction h1 {
    margin: 0 0 1.4rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.7rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
  }

  .page-introduction p {
    max-width: 1040px;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: clamp(1.08rem, 1.65vw, 1.25rem);
    line-height: 1.72;
  }

  .experience-sections {
    padding-bottom: clamp(5rem, 9vw, 8rem);
  }

  .experience-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns:
      minmax(0, 1.15fr)
      minmax(320px, 0.85fr);
    gap: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 7rem);
    align-items: start;
    padding:
      clamp(3.5rem, 6vw, 5.5rem) 0
      clamp(4rem, 7vw, 6rem);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .section-introduction {
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .section-introduction h2 {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.7vw, 3.35rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 0.9rem 0 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.08rem, 1.6vw, 1.3rem);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .section-summary {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 2rem 0 0;
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.3vw, 1.1rem);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .highlights {
    padding-top: 0.35rem;
  }

  .highlights h3 {
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.07em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .highlights ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .highlights li {
    position: relative;
    margin: 0;
    padding:
      0.95rem 0
      0.95rem 1.35rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: clamp(0.96rem, 1.2vw, 1.04rem);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .highlights li:last-child {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .highlights li::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 1.55rem;
    left: 0;
    width: 0.35rem;
    height: 0.35rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .organizations {
    margin: 1.6rem 0 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .experience-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .highlights {
      max-width: 780px;
      padding-top: 0;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .page-introduction {
      padding:
        3rem 0
        3.5rem;
    }

    .experience-section {
      gap: 2rem;
      padding:
        3rem 0
        4rem;
    }

    .section-summary {
      margin-top: 1.6rem;
    }

    .highlights li {
      padding-left: 1.15rem;
    }
  }
</style>